briefdescription.para: Administrative window for managing products and prices.

para.verbatim:
Swing window that allows administrators to: - view drinks, appetizers and main courses loaded from the backend. - add new items to each category. - update the price and name of existing items.
All data is obtained and persisted through the ProductService, which internally uses ApiClient to call the REST API.
